        {
            "title": "標普500指數歷史性漲破7000點 美股行情不再局限於科技板塊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"835\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q2NpOTpsmbwtddScrbPdiA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7d5b81842c5b29b0bd2d946f61cbe846\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 標普500指數突破重要的心理關口並首次站上7000點，投資者押注美國企業利潤將在經濟提速中獲得提振。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這個美股基準指數周三早盤上漲0.3%，達到7002.28點的紀錄高位。得益於對人工智能應用和硬體開發公司的投資，該指數2025年上漲了16%，連續第三年實現兩位數成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管科技股在人工智能晶片需求的樂觀情緒推動下助力大盤最終突破了這一里程碑，但過去幾個月的行情主要集中在材料和能源板塊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0bc4ce06-f403-31cc-aec0-a7c5be1f1cf8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近幾周來，投資者紛紛尋求分散股票配置，以期從經濟增速大幅提高的預期中獲益。原物料、能源生產商以及非必需消費品製造商的股票年初領漲大盤，延續了去年11月啟動的漲勢。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"835\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TFg6aTmZv3Cl4a.66UID.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/85f5650a1476371e5e7672b291519c50\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彼時，標普指數在10月下旬達到峰值後陷入振盪，人工智能支出之憂迫使投資者重新思考這一龐大行業的格局。標普500指數一度從10月高點下跌5.1%，但在年底反彈後又攀上新高。過去幾周的大部分時間裡，該指數一直在6900點附近徘徊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「市場自10月以來就陷在6900點上下50動彈不得，」 Truist Advisory Services首席投資官兼首席市場策略師Keith Lerner說，「突破持續兩個多月的橫盤區間的上沿」可以提振投資者情緒，並引發漂亮的技術走勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題S&amp;P 500 Climbs Above 7,000 as Stocks Rally Broadens Beyond Tech</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Matt Turner.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE500%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7%E6%BC%B2%E7%A0%B47000%E9%BB%9E-%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%A1%8C%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%B1%80%E9%99%90%E6%96%BC%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%9D%BF%E5%A1%8A-155013964.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 01:27:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國財長貝森特否認干預日圓匯率 重申強勢美元政策",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長斯科特·貝森特周三在接受CNBC採訪時，淡化了有關美國可能考慮入市拋售美元、買入日圓的猜測，重申長期奉行的「強勢美元政策」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>明確表示，美國「絕對沒有」為了提振日圓而干預匯市。在被問及美國是否可能採取此類行動時，他表示：「除了重申我們奉行強勢美元政策外，我們不作其他評論。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓匯率應聲下跌。截至紐約時間上午10:37，日圓兌美元匯率下跌約0.7%，報153.34。有報導稱紐約聯邦儲備銀行上周五對該貨幣對進行了所謂的「匯率檢查」，隨後有關美日可能聯手拋售美元、買入日圓的猜測一度激增。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7e28550f-16a6-3c77-9755-ec92f8ed934d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「美國始終奉行強勢美元政策，但這意味著要建立正確的經濟基本面，」貝森特說道，「如果我們擁有穩健的政策，資金自然會隨之流入。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，貝森特還指出，隨著美國貿易逆差的縮小，從長遠來看，美元有望自動走強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Cools Yen Intervention Speculation, Touts Strong Dollar</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A1%E9%95%B7%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E5%8C%AF%E7%8E%87-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%A2%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96-154626177.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 01:27:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
